# Local raw snapshot of Sefaria's /api/index/titles payload used by
# scripts/build-lexicon.mjs --titles-file. The build script never writes it
# into the repo (it emits only public/lexicon.json), but guard against a
# hand-saved copy being committed — the 3 MB raw snapshot is a rebuildable
# intermediate, not an asset (SPEC §L1).
titles-raw.json
*.titles-snapshot.json
